                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing lithium dihydrogen phosphate from waste lithium ion batteries",
                    "一种利用废旧锂离子电池制备磷酸二氢锂的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for preparing lithium dihydrogen phosphate by using a waste lithium ion battery. The method comprises the following steps: treating the waste lithium ion battery to obtain lithium ion battery powder; lithium ions in the lithium ion battery powder are leached through an oxidation acid leaching method by taking excessive concentrated phosphoric acid and hydrogen peroxide as an acid leaching system, and a leaching solution is obtained through filtering; taking saponified dioctyl phosphate P204 and sulfonated kerosene as extraction reagents, extracting the leachate, standing and layering into a water phase solution and an organic phase solution; and adding a trisodium phosphate solution into the aqueous phase solution for lithium precipitation to obtain a lithium phosphate precipitate, and adding strong phosphoric acid into the lithium phosphate precipitate for acidification treatment to obtain a lithium dihydrogen phosphate solution. According to the method, the lithium extraction effect on different types of waste batteries is excellent, the lithium resource in the waste batteries is converted into the battery-grade lithium dihydrogen phosphate product with high economic value through a simple process, the lithium resource of the waste batteries is fully utilized, and in the process, the three wastes are few, the energy consumption is low, and the economic cost is low."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种利用废旧锂离子电池制备磷酸二氢锂的方法，包括：将废旧锂离子电池处理得到锂离子电池粉末；以过量浓磷酸加过氧化氢作为酸浸体系通过氧化酸浸法浸出锂离子电池粉末中的锂离子，过滤得到浸出液；以皂化处理后的磷酸二辛酯P204和磺化煤油作为萃取试剂，浸出液萃取后静置分层为水相溶液和有机相溶液；往水相溶液中加入磷酸三钠溶液进行沉锂得到磷酸锂沉淀，向磷酸锂沉淀中加入浓磷酸进行酸化处理，获得磷酸二氢锂溶液。本发明方法对不同种类废旧电池的提锂效果均表现优异，通过简单的工艺将废旧电池中的锂资源转化为有高经济价值的电池级磷酸二氢锂产品，充分地利用废旧电池的锂资源，且过程中“三废”少，能耗小，经济成本低。"
                }
